2001: A Space Odyssey
1968
A contemplative exploration of near future space exploration, the perils of AI and the possiblities of non-human intelligent life
A quiet film
https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/2001:_A_Space_Odyssey

Homeworld series
1999-2024
A series of strategy games follow the last remnant of a people searching for where they came from. They rediscover clues to their past that showed they came from another world, and in the process of exploring that past their world is destroyed as they set a course among the stars towards that place their ancestors came from. 
Samuel Barber's 1936 Adagio for Strings is the definining musical theme
https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Homeworld

